rule.ruleString:
function statescodes() 
{ 
    var allRadarStates = ["US", "AS", "GM", "NL", "LU", "BE", "FR", "UK", "EI", "LS", "SZ", "AN", "MN"];
    
    return context.device !== null && 
            context.viewedLocation !== null &&
            allRadarStates.indexOf(context.viewedLocation.country) !== -1 &&
            context.weatherSummary.nearestStartPrecip !== null &&
            context.weatherSummary.observation !== null &&
            context.weatherSummary.nearestStartPrecip.eventType !== null &&
            context.weatherSummary.nearestStartPrecip.eventType !== 0 &&
            (new Date(context.weatherSummary.nearestStartPrecip.startTime) - 
                new Date(context.weatherSummary.observation.obsTime) <= 3*1000*60*60 )
}

statescodes()

function isStormForecast(){
var winterPhenomenaCode = ["BZ", "WS","LE","IS","blizzard","freezeRain","TSI", "snowSquall", "snowFall","winterStorm"]

return context.weatherSummary.nearestWinterStormAlert !== null &&
    winterPhenomenaCode.indexOf(context.weatherSummary.nearestWinterStormAlert.phenomenaCode) !== -1 &&
    ((context.weatherSummary.nearestWinterStormAlert.significanceCode == "A") || 
    (context.weatherSummary.nearestWinterStormAlert.significanceCode == "S"))
}

isStormForecast()
